videos.description: Sagaba Konate gets a pass under the basket and elevates for the slam to put West Virginia on the board.
videos.headline: Kontae throws it down early vs. TTU

videos.description: Jevon Carter uses a pump fakes around a defender and then sinks a jumper to give him nine points in the first 10 minutes.
videos.headline: Carter's jumper gives him 9 points early

videos.description: Logan Routt blocks Jarrett Culver's layup to prevent a Texas Tech basket.
videos.headline: Routt shuts down TTU with big block

videos.description: Sagaba Konate challenges Jarrett Culver at the rim to keep West Virginia's lead.
videos.headline: Konate says no with block for WVU

videos.description: Sagaba Konate gets another big block giving him nine games with five or more blocks this season.
videos.headline: Konate elevates for 100th block of the season

videos.description: Jevon Carter intercepts a pass and draws a foul on the layup to extend West Virginia's lead.
videos.headline: Carter steal leads to 3-point play for WVU

videos.description: Fran Fraschilla and Rich Hollenberg credit the play from both Jevon Carter and Daxter Miles Jr. on their senior night in the big 84-74 win over Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Fraschilla, Hollenberg credit WVU seniors in statement win over TTU
